I am a DESIGN JUNKIE! On my tombstone, it may just say... DEATH BY INSPO!! I am constantly inspired by travel, design magazines, interior designers and COLOR. COLOR. COLOR.  I rearrange furniture for fun or spontaneously paint a wall to switch things up. I can't help it... I live to create beautiful, welcoming spaces for my friends, family and also for myself to feel continuously inspired. 

So, as you can imagine, it has always been a dream of mine to launch a collection of paint for the home and I am so proud to say that #FLOWERPaint IS FINALLY HERE and with our long-time partners @Walmart .com. We are launching with 27 colors that I've selected after many, many years of searching for the perfect shades for my own spaces. 

My next project is painting my kitchen and I am really debating between so many of our new paint colors because THEY ARE ALL SO GOOD. 

What would you choose??? Feel free to vote below! I'll be sharing some of my favorite colors up next so stay tuned!!! 
All 27 of our new #FLOWERPaint colors are now available @walmart .com (link in bio). #DBKitchenReno #DesignedbyDrew
